1764:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Transmit data can be loaded to TBUF by software by writing to the transmit buffer input
