1766:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * to one of these input locations is stored in the transmit buffer TBUF. Additionally, the
1767:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * address of the written location is evaluated and can be used for additional control
1768:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * purposes. This 5-bit wide information (named Transmit Control Information TCI) can be
1769:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * used for different purposes in different protocols.
